text: John Meade may refer to: * Sir John Meade, 1st Baronet (1642–1707), Irish barrister, judge and politician, Member of the Parliament of Ireland 1689–1707 * John Meade, 1st Earl of Clanwilliam (1744–1800), Irish peer and Member of the Parliament of Ireland for Banagher 1764–67 * John Meade (British Army officer) (c. 1775–1849), Member of the UK Parliament for County Down 1805–12 * John Meade, 7th Earl of Clanwilliam (1919–2009), Anglo-Irish nobleman
title: John Meade
